    {
      "chapter_num": "1-1",
      "title": "他是她",
      "game_type": "標準選擇題",
      "description": "本章節描述小欣因穿著被質疑的故事。",
      "novel_bg": "backgrounds/chapter_1_1_bg.jpg",
      "novel_music": "music/chapter_1_1.mp3",
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "sequence": 1,
          "speaker": "旁白",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "小欣平時喜歡穿運動服，看起來和太陽班的其他女生不太一樣。",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 2,
          "speaker": "小剛",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "「小欣，妳怎麼穿得像個男生一樣？是不是穿到你弟弟的衣服了？」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 3,
          "speaker": "小欣",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "（笑了笑）「沒有啊！因為我很喜歡跑步，所以才穿運動服，這樣也比較方便，而且穿運動服很舒服！」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 4,
          "speaker": "小剛",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "「可是女生就應該穿裙子啊！妳這樣看起來很奇怪，大家都覺得妳不像女生。」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 5,
          "speaker": "旁白",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "旁邊的小晴皺起眉頭，但沒有說話，只是靜靜地看著這一切。",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 6,
          "speaker": "旁白",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "老師注意到了班上對小欣的議論，決定利用一堂健康課來討論性別特質。",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 7,
          "speaker": "老師",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "「同學們，我今天想問大家一個問題：什麼是女生應該做的，什麼是男生應該做的？」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 8,
          "speaker": "旁白",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "小剛舉手。",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 9,
          "speaker": "小剛",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "「女生應該穿裙子，男生應該穿褲子！」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 10,
          "speaker": "老師",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "「可是，有沒有人想過，這些規定是誰訂的？衣服應該是用來保護我們的身體或是裝飾打扮的，不是嗎？所以每個人都可以選擇自己喜歡的穿著，不應該性別刻板印象哦！」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 11,
          "speaker": "旁白",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "小晴舉手。",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 12,
          "speaker": "小晴",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "「老師，我也覺得小欣穿運動服沒什麼不對！」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 13,
          "speaker": "老師",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "「很好，小晴說得對。小欣穿運動服是因為她喜歡，而且跑步也比較方便，這是她的選擇。而我們應該尊重每個人的選擇，對不對？」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 14,
          "speaker": "旁白",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "幾天後的體育課，小剛發現小欣跑步比班上的所有人都快。",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 15,
          "speaker": "小剛",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "「哇，小欣，妳真的跑得好快！怎麼做到的？」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 16,
          "speaker": "小欣",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "（微笑）「因為我很喜歡跑步，所以每天放學後都會留下來練習。」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 17,
          "speaker": "小剛",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "（靦腆地說）「原來如此！對不起，我之前嘲笑妳穿運動服。其實我覺得妳很酷！」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        },
        {
          "sequence": 18,
          "speaker": "小欣",
          "character_left": null,
          "character_right": null,
          "text": "「沒關係，希望大家知道，衣服或外貌不能定義一個人。我只是在做自己而已。」",
          "bg_img": null,
          "voice": null,
          "bg_music": null
        }
